which dynamically loads the lib (so/dll) and thereby the symbols."

 (format t "~%=============================================~%")
 (format t "LOAD  COORDINATION  INTERFACE --> ~s~%" name)
 (format t "=============================================~%")

 (let ((ptr nil)
       (resultList nil)
